{"an7.3:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.3 ","an7.3:0.2":"1. Dhanavagga ","an7.3:0.3":"Sankhittabalasutta ","an7.3:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","an7.3:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame …pe… ","an7.3:1.3":"sattimani, bhikkhave, balani. ","an7.3:1.4":"Katamani satta? ","an7.3:1.5":"Saddhabalam, viriyabalam, hiribalam, ottappabalam, satibalam, samadhibalam, pannabalam. ","an7.3:1.6":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, satta balaniti. ","an7.3:2.1":"Saddhabalam viriyanca, ","an7.3:2.2":"hiri ottappiyam balam; ","an7.3:2.3":"Satibalam samadhi ca, ","an7.3:2.4":"panna ve sattamam balam; ","an7.3:2.5":"Etehi balava bhikkhu, ","an7.3:2.6":"sukham jivati pandito. ","an7.3:3.1":"Yoniso vicine dhammam, ","an7.3:3.2":"pannayattham vipassati; ","an7.3:3.3":"Pajjotasseva nibbanam, ","an7.3:3.4":"vimokkho hoti cetaso”ti. ","an7.3:3.5":"Tatiyam. "}